       </strong>
       ) tandem Tudor domains and H3K4me3 peptide. The Sgf29 tandem Tudor domains are shown in cartoon representation and coloured in blue. The H3K4me3 peptide is shown as a stick model. The conserved and non-conserved hydrogen bonds are coloured in red and black, respectively. (
       <strong>
