     </em>
     Δ
     <em>
      0 ura3
     </em>
     Δ
     <em>
      0 YCL010c∷kanMX4
     </em>
     ) and its isogenic parent strain BY4742 (
     <em>
      MAT
     </em>
     α
     <em>
      his3
     </em>
     Δ
     <em>
      1 leu2
     </em>
